":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1445b40264211a2d074855689d06b47e6fd52f01","tid":2277562,"uid":26360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1319e3112bb1d9c57c3fdc64e08ffeee5744f022","tid":2277562,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"睇完physio<br />\n之後的起心肝入gym room啦<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"我見好多動作屋企都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:46:34.000Z","msg":"有無YouTube link"},{"pid":"ff676e546b4ea736e79407973d1aaa4a1dd2e753","tid":2277562,"uid":1697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1445b40264211a2d074855689d06b47e6fd52f01","tid":2277562,"uid":26360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1319e3112bb1d9c57c3fdc64e08ffeee5744f022","tid":2277562,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"睇完physio<br />\n之後的起心肝入gym room啦<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"我見好多動作屋企都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T01:01:39.000Z","msg":"你呢D問題都黎自於日常生活姿勢唔正確<br />\n用body weight 去做唔係唔得 但我相信你最多都係做到舒緩only 如果有1,2星期停左冇做就打回原形<br />\n<br />\n其實一般人冇做負重訓練 肌肉量都會不足 搞到日常生活維持一個良好姿勢都好辛苦 因為你對自己既肌肉都冇認識 唔識控制佢地 搞到支撐唔起<br />\n<br />\n唔係練到好多肌肉先有用 而係重訓既動作其實都會應用係日常生活上 等你習慣用到岩既肌肉去完成平時既野 例如蹲低起身 彎腰拎野 長期坐office 點先令自己舒服D<br />\n當然去到進一步 你練到有肌肉果時 相信除左有好既體態之外 你行步路都輕鬆好多<br />\n<br />\n如果上網睇youtube就有效 咁周街D人都firm到仆街啦<br />\n加油啦..."},{"pid":"71a6dcea3b84e5ebc007d688a05cda00b01451e0","tid":2277562,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4e91cd161c182a8469106e2413cfae4ec7261ee","tid":2277562,"uid":26360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"408bc92a14b063073fc1b7a3baf2fc0b5c47835b","tid":2277562,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T17:45:41.000Z","msg":"我只係去公園做，做引體上升，做Hanging leg raise"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:43:15.000Z","msg":"我想整好個翼狀肩胛先，引體好似冇咩用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"當然唔係，肩胛骨穩定性係你需要嘅嘢，即係有mobility 自由轉動，有力向中間夾，有力向下壓，而引體上升正正亦需要，未有能力做引體上升之前，正需要重點練呢個部位，例如練好下圖呢個先，呢個動作如果你未夠力拉上，你可以做直手版本，只用肩胛骨做，其實就算你去健身房，你都要首先練返強肩胛骨穩定性先架啦，如果唔係，負重鍛鍊時點保護膊頭，你去邊度練都冇得回避呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqcMHYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqcMHYn.jpg&h=5f4a457e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3690abba1556ccf61202ae143f90ec5238b959a7","tid":2277562,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:34:05.000Z","msg":"每人去廁所都做幾十下深蹲,屋企做下push up就得<br />\n做gym浪費時間"},{"pid":"cc31195a2de20cbbf3b43bfebeb9f92f649e0eae","tid":2277562,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"買條橡筋彈力帶 感受左肩胛肌肉用力嘅感覺先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你依家做咩重訓都冇用 一定會用左其他肌肉代償<br />\n<br />\n其實最快方法係搵健身教練 幫你feel到肌肉用力嘅情況下去做重訓"},{"pid":"e21d7bbd082e141cd143b8295639c0dc4468ecb8","tid":2277562,"uid":26360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4208a28fc4b8ebb95950a3e825c96689e31de2e","tid":2277562,"uid":197441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1445b40264211a2d074855689d06b47e6fd52f01","tid":2277562,"uid":26360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1319e3112bb1d9c57c3fdc64e08ffeee5744f022","tid":2277562,"uid":1697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"睇完physio<br />\n之後的起心肝入gym room啦<br />\n唉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"我見好多動作屋企都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T00:46:34.000Z","msg":"有無YouTube link"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CEiqDwif3b4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCEiqDwif3b4&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7yrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfR